rounds.response:
I need to create two potential winning lines in my next move, forcing a guaranteed win no matter how Player 1 responds.

Currently:
- I already have O at 4 (center) and 8.
- Next move I can threaten both:
  – the lower row (6,7,8) by placing at 6 or 7, or
  – the middle column (1,4,7) by placing at 1 or 7.

Crucially, cell 7 lets me fork: it would complete (7,4,8) vertically at the same time as (6,7,8) horizontally, giving me two simultaneous threats that can’t both be blocked.

[7]
